data.message: Phase 4.4 Production Testing - complete session: Completed both synthetic episode test and real production test (The Fashanus Episode 1). Eval pipeline validated. Produced 35-sec video at $0 cost. User feedback: technically works but emotionally flat - need consistent characters, real voice acting, music. Key learning: pipeline works, craft needs more.
